산재예방(산재),재해예방기관 설립 법인 요건,2016-12-05 13:23:32.0,윤정인,,1,34,@DataType:Clob,"<p class=""0"" style=""line-height:150%; margin-right:5pt; margin-left:5pt; mso-pagination:none;text-autospace:none;mso-padding-alt:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;""><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;"">재해예방전문지도기관을 지정받을 수 있는 자로는 법 제</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;"">52</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;"">조의 </span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;"">4</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;"">에 따라 등록한 산업안전지도사</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;"">(</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;"">전기안전 또는 건설안전분야의 산업안전지도사만 해당한다</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;"">), </span><u style=""text-underline:#000000 single""><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0pt;"">재해예방 업무를 하려는 법인</span></u><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;"">으로 
규정하고 있는데,</span></p><p class=""0"" style=""line-height:150%; margin-right:5pt; margin-left:5pt; mso-pagination:none;text-autospace:none;mso-padding-alt:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;""><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;"">“1</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;"">인 법인</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;"">”</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;"">이란  대표이사 </span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;"">1</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;"">인으로 법인을 설립하는 법인도 
상기의 재해예방 업무를 하려는 법인으로 볼 수 있을까요??</span></p>
<p class=""0"" style=""line-height:150%; margin-right:5pt; margin-left:5pt;"">&nbsp;</p>
