<p>ㅇ 산업안전보건법 제36조 제4항(안전검사 미실시 기계 기구 사용 금지)</p>
<p>이 경우 과태료 부과시 각각 적용해야 하는지, 하나만 적용하여야 하는지 궁금합니다.</p>
<p>ㅇ <span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">질서위반행위규제법 제</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">13</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">조</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">(</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">수개의 질서위반행위의 처리</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">) </span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-hansi-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">① </span><u style=""text-underline:#000000 single""><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">하나의 행위가 </span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">2 </span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">이상의 질서위반행위에 해당하는 경우</span></u><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">에는 각 질서위반행위에 대하여 정한 과태료 중 가장 중한 과태료를 부과한다</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">.</span></p>
<p class=""0"" style=""mso-pagination:none;text-autospace:none;mso-padding-alt:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;"">  &nbsp;  <span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-hansi-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">② </span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">제</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">1</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">항의 경우를 제외하고 </span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">2 </span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">이상의 질서위반행위가 경합하는 경우에는 각 질서위반행위에 대하여 정한 과태료를 각각 부과한다</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">. </span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">다만</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">, </span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">다른 법령</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">(</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">지방자치단체의 조례를 포함한다</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">. </span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">이하 같다</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-fami","ly:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">)</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">에 특별한 규정이 있는 경우에는 그 법령으로 정하는 바에 따른다</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">.</span></p>␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀",,,
산재예방(산재),사다리/계단 판단 기준,2015-05-28 16:54:41.0,윤정인,안전난간설치여부2.jpg,1,58,@DataType:Clob,"<p>ㅇ 산업안전보건기준에 관한 규칙 제3장-- 통로</p>
<p>ㅇ 24조 사다리식 통로, 26조 계단 규정이 있는데,</p>
<p>ㅇ 붙임(파일)과 같은 형태의 것은 계단에 해당되는지, 사다리에 해당되는지 질의합니다.</p>
<p>&nbsp;= 결론적으로 어떤 통로가 계단인지, 사다리에 해당하는지에 대하여는 무엇을 
기준으로 구분할 수 있을 지요.....</p>
<p>= 둘다 기능적인 측면에서는 별다른 차이가 없는 것 같은데요</p>
