산재예방(산재),산업안전보건법 제31조 및 제32조 관련 질의,2015-01-23 08:26:07.0,윤정인,,1,10,@DataType:Clob,"<p>ㅇ &nbsp;<span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">산업안전보건법 제</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">31</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">조의 규정에 의거 사업주는 해당 사업장의 근로자에 대하여 고용노동부령이 정하는 바에 따라 정기적으로 안전</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-hansi-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">?</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">보건에 관한 교육을 하여야 한다고 규정하고 있으며</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">,</span></p>
<p class=""0"" style=""text-indent:-18.9pt; line-height:180%; mso-pagination:none;text-autospace:none;mso-padding-alt:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;"">  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ㅇ 
<span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-hansi-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;""> </span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">산업안전보건법 제</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">32</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">조의 규정에 의거 다음의 각호의 자는 고용노동부장관이 실시하는 안전</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">, </span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">보건에 관한 직무교육을 받아야 한다고 규정하고 있으며</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">, </span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">각호의 자는 관리책임자</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">, </span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">제</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">15</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">조에 따른 안전관리자 및 제</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">16</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">조에 따른 보건관리자</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">, </span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">재해예방전문기관의 종사자가 해당됩니다</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">. 
</span></p>
<p class=""0"" style=""text-indent:-18.9pt; line-height:180%;""><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ㅇ 
그런데, </span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">시행규칙 제</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffff","ff;"">33</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">조 </span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">2 </span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">규정에 따른 안전보건교육의 면제는 산업안전보건법 제</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">31</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">조 제</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">4</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">항에 따라 
관리감독자에게는 적용되는데, 안전관리자</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">, </span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">관리책임자</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">, </span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">보건관리자</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">, </span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">재해예방전문기관 종사자는 
적용되지 않습니다.</span></p>
<p class=""0"" style=""text-indent:-18.9pt; line-height:180%;""><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">ㅇ 
&nbsp;- 이와 관련하여 산업안전보건법 제31조의 안전관리자(보건관리자)는 근로자의 
안전보건교육을 실시할 수 있는자에 해당되는 데,</span></p>
<p class=""0"" style=""text-indent:-18.9pt; line-height:180%;""><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">- 
&nbsp;&nbsp;- 이처럼 안전관리자(보건관리자)가 산업안전보건법 제32조의 직무교육을 
받는 것과 별도로 산업안전보건법 제31조의 정기안전보건교육을 받아야 하는지에 
대하여 이견이 있어 질의합니다.</span></p>
<p class=""0"" style=""text-indent:-18.9pt; line-height:180%;""><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;갑설&gt; 
산업안전보건법 제31조는 모든 근로자에 해당하므로 보건관리자(안전관리자)도 정기안전보건교육을 
받아야 한다.</span></p>
<p class=""0"" style=""text-indent:-18.9pt; line-height:180%;"">&nbsp;</p>
<p class=""0"" style=""text-indent:-18.9pt; line-height:180%;""><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;을설&gt; 
산업안전보건법 제32조의 대상자는 보수교육을 받으므로 산업안전보건법 제31조의 
정기안전보건교육 대상이 아니다.</span></p>
<p class=""0"" style=""text-indent:-18.9pt; line-height:180%;""><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>
