산재예방(산재),산업안전보건기준에 관한 규칙 제27조(계단의 폭) 관련 질의,2015-01-14 16:33:13.0,윤정인,,1,18,@DataType:Clob,"<p>ㅇ 산업안전보건 기준에 관한 규칙 제27조의 규정에 의거 사업주는 계단을 설치하는 
경우 그 폭을 1미터 이상으로 하여야 한다.(단서조항 생략)고 되어 있고,</p>
<p>ㅇ <span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">건축물의 피난</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-hansi-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">ㆍ</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">방화구조 등의 기준에 관한 규칙</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">(</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">국토교통부령</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">) </span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">제</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">15</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">조의 계단의 설치기준을 
정하고 있습니다.(아래 규정)</span></p>
<p><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">제</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">1</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">항의 규정에 의하여 계단을 설치하는 경우 계단 및 계단참의 너비</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">(</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">옥내계단에 한한다</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">), </span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">계단의 단높이 및 단너비의 칫수는 다음 각호의 기준에 적합하여야 한다</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">. </span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">이 경우 돌음계단의 단너비는 그 좁은 너비의 끝부분으로부터 </span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">30</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">센티미터의 위치에서 측정한다</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">. &nbsp;&lt;</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">개정 </span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">2003.1.6., 2005.7.22., 2010.4.7.&gt;</span></p>
<p class=""0"" style=""mso-pagination:none;text-autospace:none;mso-padding-alt:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;""><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">1. </span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">초등학교의 계단인 경우에는 계단 및 계단참의 너비는 </span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">150</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">센티미터 이상</span><span lang=""EN-US"" st","yle=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">, </span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">단높이는 </span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">16</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">센티미터 이하</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">, </span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">단너비는 </span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">26</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">센티미터 이상으로 할 것</span>  </p><p class=""0"" style=""mso-pagination:none;text-autospace:none;mso-padding-alt:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;""><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">2. </span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">중</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">&middot;</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">고등학교의 계단인 경우에는 계단 및 계단참의 너비는 </span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">150</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">센티미터 이상</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">, </span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">단높이는 </span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">18</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">센티미터 이하</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">, </span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">단너비는 </span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">26</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">센티미터 이상으로 할 것</span>  </p><p class=""0"" style=""mso-pagination:none;text-autospace:none;mso-padding-alt:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;""><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">3. </span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">문화 및 집회시설</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">(</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">공연장</span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">&middot;</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">집회장 및 관람장에 한한다</span><span lang=""EN-U","S"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">)&middot;</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">판매시설 기타 이와 유사한 용도에 쓰이는 건축물의 계단인 경우에는 계단 및 계단참의 너비를 </span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">120</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">센티미터 이상으로 할 것</span></p><p class=""0"" style=""mso-pagination:none;text-autospace:none;mso-padding-alt:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;"">  &nbsp;  <span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">4. </span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">윗층의 거실의 바닥면적의 합계가 </span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">200</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">제곱미터 이상이거나 거실의 바닥면적의 합계가 </span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">100</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">제곱미터 이상인 지하층의 계단인 경우에는 계단 및 계단참의 너비를 </span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">120</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">센티미터 이상으로 할 것</span>&nbsp;  </p><p class=""0"" style=""mso-pagination:none;text-autospace:none;mso-padding-alt:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;""><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">5. </span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">기타의 계단인 경우에는 계단 및 계단참의 너비를 </span><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">60</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">센티미터 이상으로 할 것</span>&nbsp;  </p><p class=""0"" style=""mso-pagination:none;text-autospace:none;mso-padding-alt:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;""><span lang=""EN-US"" style=""font-family:휴먼명조;mso-ascii-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">6. </span><u style=""text-underline:#000000 single""><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-hansi-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0pt;color:#0000ff;background:#ffffff;"">「</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0pt;color:#0000ff;background:#ffffff;"">산업안전보건법</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-hansi-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0pt;color:#0000ff;background:#ffffff;"">」</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">에 의한 작업장에 설치하는 계단인 경우에는 </span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-hansi-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0pt;color:#0000ff;background:#ffffff;"">「</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0pt;color:#0000ff;background:#ffffff;"">산업안전 기준에 관한 규칙</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-hansi-font-family:휴먼명조;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0pt;color:#0000ff;b","ackground:#ffffff;"">」</span><span style=""mso-fareast-font-family:휴먼명조;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0pt;background:#ffffff;"">에서 정한 구조로 할 것</span></u></p><p class=""0"" style=""background-color:white; mso-pagination:none;text-autospace:none;mso-padding-alt:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;"">  &nbsp;</p>
<p class=""0"" style=""background-color:white;"">&nbsp;이 경우 건축물의 기준에 5호에 
따라 기타의 계단의 경우 계단의 너비를 60센티미터 이상으로 하여 국토부 기준에 
부합하는 건축물이 있는데,</p>
<p class=""0"" style=""background-color:white;"">이 건축물을 산업안전보건법에 의한 
작업장이 될 경우에도 동 산업안전보건기준에 관한 규칙 제27조에 따라 그 폭을 &nbsp;1미터 
